# .env-example — placeholder for environment variables.
#
# This project has no external API calls (see ADR-001-gatekeeper-na.md),
# so no secrets are required for v1.00.
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values if secrets are added in future
# milestones (e.g. remote experiment tracking, cloud storage).
#
# EXAMPLE_SECRET=your_value_here
